headline: West to Host First-Quarter 2025 Conference Call
summary: West Pharmaceutical Services, Inc. (NYSE: WST), a global leader in innovative solutions for injectable drug administration, today announced that it will release first-quarter financial results before the market opens on Thursday, April 24, 2025, and will follow with a conference call to discuss the results and business expectations at 9:00 a.m. Eastern Time.
